replyContent:
I'm sorry you've had problems finding your surgery on the app. Please get in touch with our support team through the app, or at hello@well.co.uk and they'll be able to help. 
Unfortunately, we're only able to offer this service to people with GPs in England – we've updated our store listing to make this clearer.
